ant of <b>Daud</b> or <b>Dowd</b>, the former arising from the Middle English personal name <i>Daud(e)</i>, an extended form of   Daw  , and the latter from the Middle English personal name <i>Doude</i>, perhaps a side-form of either <i>Dodde</i> or of <i>Daude</i>, a pet form of   Ralph  ."]},{"name":"Dutson","meanings":["variant of   Dodson   with devoicing of the second consonant before voiceless /s/.","variant of <b>Dudson</b>, itself either a variant of   Dodson   or a habitational name from Dudston in Shropshire, with the assimilation of <i>-t-</i>.","English:"]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Dodson was born in 1490, in Mildenhall, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom. He married Agneta \"Agnes\" Alice Richards Of Marriot White in 1510, in Suffolk, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1588, in Suffolk, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 98."},"et":{"1490–1588":"1490–1588","1495–1549":"1495–1549","1510–1590":"1510–1590","1588":"1588","1510":"1510","July 1549":"juuli 1549","1495":"1495","1590":"1590","1490":"1490","1549":"1549","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fi":{"1490–1588":"1490–1588","1495–1549":"1495–1549","1510–1590":"1510–1590","1588":"1588","1510":"1510","July 1549":"heinäkuu 1549","1495":"1495","1590":"1590","1490":"1490","1549":"1549","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fr":{"1490–1588":"1490–1588","1495–1549":"1495–1549","1510–1590":"1510–1590","1588":"1588","1510":"1510","July 1549":"juillet 1549","1495":"1495","1590":"1590","1490":"1490","1549":"1549","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"John Dodson est né 